easy enough to determine growth. This is less obvious with a higher
dimensional model. Additionally, we might be interested in the following
questions: </p>


<p><ul> <li> <p> Will the population grow? </p> </li> <li> <p> If it
grows, how fast is it going to grow? </p> </li> <li> <p> What is the
balance between reproductive and non-reproductive dandelions in the
population? </p> </li> </ul></p>


